This hack simply makes video recording resolution higher in the Camera.app for 3GS users.

INSTALLATION [Requires prior knowledge of afc2add or SSH]:

1. Download the hackedframeworks.ZIP package.
2. Take the contents of the CFramework folder and put them in "/System/Library/PrivateFrameworks/Celestial.framework/N88/" overwriting the existing files. (Backup advised!)
3. Take the contents of the AVFramework folder and put them in "/System/Library/Frameworks/AVFoundation.framework/N88/" overwriting the existing file(s). (Backup advised!)
4. Reload SpringBoard.

Credits: 
HypeZ in the comments on http://blog.mikepan.com for enlightening me with the location of this new second check folder.